咗維也納公約原文做basis比大家燃五毛<br />\n樓主麻煩pin一pin<br />\n<br />\n淨係quote有關嗰兩個clause:<br />\n<br />\n第九條  <br />\n一、接受國得隨時不具解釋通知派遣國宣告使館館長或使館任何<br />\n            外交職員為不受歡迎人員或使館任何其他職員為不能接受。<br />\n            遇此情形，派遣國應斟酌情況召回該員或終止其在使館中之<br />\n            職務。任何人員得於其到達接受國國境前，被宣告為不受歡<br />\n            迎或不能接受。<br />\n        二、如派遣國拒絕或不在相當期間內履行其依本條第一項規定所<br />\n            負義務，接受國得拒絕承認該員為使館人員。 <br />\n<br />\n第十二條 <br />\n派遣國非經接受國事先明示同意，不得在使館本身所在地以外<br />\n          之地點設立辦事處，作為使館之一部分。 <br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?pcode=Y0000055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flaw.moj.gov.tw%2FLawClass%2FLawAll.aspx%3Fpcode%3DY0000055&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=b7355632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?pcode=Y0000055</a><br />\n<br />\n美國即係將喺houston設館嘅consent revoke咗，同埋可能將houston大使館嘅staff全部列作&quot;不受歡迎或不能接受&quot;<br />\n<br />\n覺得有錯請討論，我唔係法律燃"},{"pid":"20be23b118894c4a9862b4365b1d08aadf5ee2c0","tid":2124591,"uid":289134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T14:32:31.000Z","msg":"我支持唔走"},{"pid":"6823df04e60692ca01746e48ab8bacde494d6bde","tid":2124591,"uid":142824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T14:32:34.000Z","msg":"走住黎屌"},{"pid":"4c2a5e64373c3509034f38e7667f6f836e953329","tid":2124591,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"中英聯合聲明下嘅基本法乃香港特區財產，共產黨國安法強闖違反國際公約？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fda85d51f2a0af236ed1ca13dd64ba61a096e32","tid":2124591,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UqZ4mNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUqZ4mNE.jpg&h=8cbfa506&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a495276d41d4e2ba3caff80c92f966a553c986e3","tid":2124591,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0